WEBVTT

00:04.040 --> 00:05.450
[Ryn]
Previously on Siren.

00:05.460 --> 00:07.280
You're the one who had me

00:07.290 --> 00:09.326
abducted in a parking lot.

00:09.330 --> 00:12.288
What we need, you and I,
is some honesty.

00:12.290 --> 00:15.168
Okay, since
we're being honest,

00:15.170 --> 00:17.161
did your people
kill my father?

00:17.170 --> 00:18.285
You're military.

00:18.290 --> 00:20.076
Was sleeping with me
part of the job?

00:20.080 --> 00:21.456
