all on my own.

00:21.460 --> 00:24.202
[Xander] This feels good,
you and me.

00:24.210 --> 00:25.279
Letsleave
all that crap In the past.

00:25.290 --> 00:27.246
This man is a Pownall.

00:27.250 --> 00:30.287
He's a descendant of Charles
who killed our kind.

00:30.290 --> 00:33.498
You don't tell me
before about your family.

00:33.500 --> 00:36.412
Ben's family kill
because they are angry.

00:36.420 --> 00:38.411
Murder.

00:38.420 --> 00:42.038
