01:39.500 --> 01:41.115
Raised by wolves

01:41.120 --> 01:43.076
Independent

01:43.080 --> 01:44.456
[Maddie] You know this isn't
what she wants, right?

01:44.460 --> 01:46.416
_ To be
With someone else.

01:46.420 --> 01:50.208
She-- She's just trying
to save her people.

01:51.380 --> 01:53.371
[Ben]
It's more than that.

01:53.380 --> 01:56.577
Something happened
at the ranch.

01:56.580 --> 01:59.287
Ryn found out
about my family,

01:59.290 --> 02:01.531
what they did.

02:01.540 --> 02:03.110
Civilized

02:03.120 --> 02:05.372
But a little restless

02:05.380 --> 02:08.531
She thinks that I was
trying to hide it from her.

02:08.540 --> 02:10.531
[sighs]

02:10.540 --> 02:12.280
Were you?

02:15.120 --> 02:16.200
I don't know.

02:17.330 --> 02:19.378
But I need your love

02:19.380 --> 02:20.529
Maybe.

02:24.420 --> 02:26.411
You guys have got to talk.

02:26.420 --> 02:29.207
When she gets back,
you'll explain it to her.

02:30.250 --> 02:32.161
[screaming]

02:32.170 --> 02:34.570
But I need your love

02:34.580 --> 02:37.242
[Ben] If she comes
back pregnant,

02:37.250 --> 02:39.571
we'll have to hide her
from the military.

02:39.580 --> 02:42.162
And her baby. I mean,

02:42.170 --> 02:44.570
they'd never let them
go back in the water.

02:44.580 --> 02:47.413
[Ryn panting]

02:49.460 --> 02:54.159
Oh, but I need your love

