03:13.330 --> 03:15.378
[high-pitched call]

03:18.460 --> 03:20.371
[door bell jingles]

03:24.500 --> 03:26.491
Xander McClure?
Up before noon?

03:26.500 --> 03:28.320
[chuckles]

03:30.250 --> 03:31.239
What's wrong?

03:35.210 --> 03:37.610
[somber music]

04:10.420 --> 04:12.285
This was my mother's.

04:13.500 --> 04:15.411
She was buried in it?

04:15.420 --> 04:16.569
Yeah.

04:18.250 --> 04:20.411
Who would do this?

04:25.620 --> 04:27.497
Why don't you
drop me at the lab?

04:27.500 --> 04:29.411
The results of
the ocean water test
might be ready.

04:29.420 --> 04:30.705
I'll deal
with Commander Kyle.

04:30.710 --> 04:32.496
[Ben] I'll cover the Center.

04:47.750 --> 04:50.412
[beeps, cuff inflates]

05:18.670 --> 05:20.319
I am back.

05:20.330 --> 05:21.661
Ryn?

05:32.330 --> 05:33.490
I missed you.

05:33.500 --> 05:34.569
Where's Maddie?

05:36.420 --> 05:39.662
She is at the military lab.

05:43.670 --> 05:45.456
You call her.

05:53.330 --> 05:54.490
[line ringing]

05:55.620 --> 05:56.700
Hey.

05:56.710 --> 05:58.496
Good news.

05:58.500 --> 05:59.455
Ryn's back.

05:59.460 --> 06:00.700
So, did they--

06:00.710 --> 06:03.577
She wanted me to call you.

06:07.710 --> 06:09.371
I am back.

06:09.380 --> 06:11.416
How was it
out there with Levi?

06:11.420 --> 06:12.660
I mate.

06:12.670 --> 06:15.537
With others, too.

06:15.540 --> 06:16.746
Am not with baby.

06:16.750 --> 06:18.820
You know that already?

06:18.830 --> 06:20.536
Yes, I can tell.

06:20.540 --> 06:22.576
Body change with baby, and

06:22.580 --> 06:24.457
no change.

06:24.460 --> 06:25.666
Ryn, I'm so sorry.

06:25.670 --> 06:29.822
[somber music]

06:53.710 --> 06:55.496
Where's Ryn?

06:55.500 --> 06:56.876
Ryn's back in the water.

06:56.880 --> 06:59.496
I thought that you and Ben
were managing her.

06:59.500 --> 07:01.877
She goes back
from time to time to refresh.

07:01.880 --> 07:04.576
-She'll be back soon.
-Okay.

07:04.580 --> 07:07.572
Oh, uh, your ocean water
tests came back.

07:07.580 --> 07:10.788
We're interested
in the fertility research
you've been doing.

07:10.790 --> 07:14.419
Understanding
their reproduction is
quite important to us.

07:16.750 --> 07:18.786
[Maddie] I told him
she was back in the ocean.

07:18.790 --> 07:20.701
Not sure he bought it.

07:20.710 --> 07:22.610
How's she doing?

07:22.620 --> 07:24.781
She's just sleeping off
the transition.

07:24.790 --> 07:27.577
She wants me to
drop her off at Helen's
when she wakes up.

07:27.580 --> 07:28.615
I'll meet you
over there.

07:28.620 --> 07:29.780
All right, see you soon.

07:50.460 --> 07:52.872
[ominous music]

08:04.830 --> 08:08.789
[Ryn's Siren song playing]

08:23.830 --> 08:28.665
[muffled Siren song
playing through headphones]

08:29.710 --> 08:30.916
[door closes]

08:37.620 --> 08:38.609
[Xander] Ben.

08:45.790 --> 08:46.825
Ben.

08:47.830 --> 08:48.956
You okay, man?
You were just--

08:50.880 --> 08:52.609
[song stops]

08:52.620 --> 08:54.702
I was, uh,

08:54.710 --> 08:57.611
doing some baseline stats
for a study.

08:57.620 --> 08:59.668
-Baseline stats?
-Yeah.

08:59.670 --> 09:01.820
I'm gonna go ahead
and call bullshit on that.

09:02.920 --> 09:04.660
It looks like you were just

09:04.670 --> 09:07.958
listening to Ryn's
mind control shit again.

09:07.960 --> 09:09.996
You gotta cut
that crap off, man.

09:10.000 --> 09:11.786
It's messin'
with your head.

09:11.790 --> 09:14.782
So what brings you here,

09:14.790 --> 09:15.996
other than the lecture?

09:16.000 --> 09:16.989
I, um...

09:19.040 --> 09:21.031
I did something
I shouldn't have.

09:21.040 --> 09:22.200
What were you thinking,

09:22.210 --> 09:23.245
bringing a reporter
to the graveyard?

09:23.250 --> 09:26.287
I wasn't thinking, okay?

09:26.290 --> 09:28.030
I was just desperate
to get him off my back,

09:28.040 --> 09:29.246
and I wanted
to protect you guys.

09:29.250 --> 09:30.376
What did you
expect him to do?

09:30.380 --> 09:32.075
I don't know, okay?

09:32.080 --> 09:33.957
I just thought
showing him the graves

09:33.960 --> 09:36.997
would be enough, somehow.
Okay, it was stupid.

09:37.000 --> 09:39.286
-But now I just want
to figure out who did it.
-We know who did it.

09:39.290 --> 09:41.167
Nicole would've never
let that happen.

09:41.170 --> 09:42.319
She's a good person.

09:42.330 --> 09:45.163
Xan, she's not in control
of this thing.

09:57.120 --> 10:00.112
You haven't told her
about her snster's grave?

10:01.210 --> 10:03.371
No. Not yet.

10:05.170 --> 10:07.161
I'll tell her later
when we're alone.

10:14.080 --> 10:15.160
I missed you.

10:15.170 --> 10:16.410
I missed you, too.

10:16.420 --> 10:18.240
Something is wrong?

10:19.250 --> 10:20.990
I think we found out

10:21.000 --> 10:23.412
why you and the others
aren't getting pregnant.

10:23.420 --> 10:25.285
The ocean water
test results came In.

10:25.290 --> 10:27.167
They're not good.

10:27.170 --> 10:30.116
What is wrong with water?

10:30.120 --> 10:32.281
-It's polluted.
-There are substances,

10:32.290 --> 10:35.077
BPAs, from garbage,
plastics...

10:35.080 --> 10:37.457
Causing fertility problems,
just like we thought.

10:37.460 --> 10:39.325
No babies in water.

10:41.080 --> 10:42.069
No.

10:42.080 --> 10:44.207
BPAs from the water

10:44.210 --> 10:45.416
pass out of the body
in about 24 hours.

10:45.420 --> 10:49.493
But they breathe
the water like air.

10:49.500 --> 10:51.456
They're constantly
exposed to it.

10:51.460 --> 10:56.159
Not if she mates on land.
In human form.

10:59.040 --> 11:00.280
Who did you have in mind?

11:09.290 --> 11:12.111
[ominous music]

11:24.040 --> 11:25.029
[knock on door]

11:34.670 --> 11:35.329
Ryn?

11:35.830 --> 11:36.819
Hello, Helen.

11:38.880 --> 11:40.666
Who is this?

11:40.670 --> 11:44.663
I could not find Levi,
so I bring him to mate.

11:47.500 --> 11:48.535
He has no words.

11:48.540 --> 11:49.825
He is new to land.

11:49.830 --> 11:51.570
Yes, I see.

11:51.580 --> 11:53.912
I know him from water.

11:53.920 --> 11:55.490
Born when I was born.

11:55.500 --> 11:56.740
[sniffing]

12:02.750 --> 12:05.662
