12:15.750 --> 12:16.910
Must wait.

12:18.000 --> 12:18.989
Too soon.

12:21.880 --> 12:22.915
Tomorrow.

12:22.920 --> 12:24.740
[soft hiss]

12:28.000 --> 12:31.743
["Olalla" by Blanco White
playing in The Anchor]

12:31.750 --> 12:35.993
Somebody told me to believe

12:36.000 --> 12:39.538
In better times

12:41.000 --> 12:47.781
From Olalla
